      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="29356518">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/SaberMelancholy/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u53357615-57.jpg" alt="李可笑" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/29356518/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/29356518/" class="">第121页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/SaberMelancholy/" class=" " title="李可笑">李可笑</a>
                (各人投其好，各自不相干)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="29356518">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">万物皆有死，
柔软的东西因躯体柔软而不免于死，
易碎的东西因结构易碎而不免于死；
中空的东西则由于身体多孔而必死……
</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-11-15 00:11</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">2人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>万物皆有死，
柔软的东西因躯体柔软而不免于死，
易碎的东西因结构易碎而不免于死；
中空的东西则由于身体多孔而必死……
</q></blockquote>
