              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">用铜器击着铜器，叫魔王不能把他抢走去吞食


Saturn可不是Satan</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-07-31 09:48</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>用铜器击着铜器，叫魔王不能把他抢走去吞食</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Saturn可不是Satan
